name: 雛菜
text:
ね、どうしよう
もう終わっちゃうけど～？
trans:
Hey, what should we do?
The live's ended already~?

name: 円香
text: じゃ、みなさん入場からやり直しってことで
trans:
Then, how about we re-do it from when the fans
enter the hall?

name: 小糸
text:
で、でも……
今日がちゃんと終わらないと
trans:
B-But...
If we don't end today's stage properly,

name: 小糸
text:
次が……
始まらないよね……？
trans:
We...
We wouldn't be able to start the next live,
right...?

name: 雛菜
text:
あは～！
雛菜、次のライブでしたいこともう考えてる！
trans:
Aha~!
Hinana's already thinking about what she wants to do
for the next live!

name: 円香
text: それなら、まずは終わろう
trans: In that case, then let's end the live.
